 *
 * $Date: 2004/03/05 21:58:51 $ $Revision: 1.1.9.2 $
 * $Header: /cvs/src/X-Window/xc/extras/ogl-sample/main/gfx/lib/glu/libnurbs/internals/patch.cc,v 1.1.9.2 2004/03/05 21:58:51 tg Exp $
